{"tid":1704062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角2008年高空投擲腐蝕性液體傷人案，至今仍然無拉到人","createTime":"2019-11-10T14:17:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T14:26:13.000Z","uid":230104,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bc1c8a938920a849f0aa19fa680d4757fa90b8a6","tid":1704062,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"旺角高空投擲腐蝕性液體傷人案，是發生在香港旺角西洋菜南街一帶的一連串高空投擲腐蝕性液體傷人案件（香港傳媒多以「鏹水彈」[1]稱之）。由2008年12月起至2009年6月，共發生了3宗同類案件，導致合共100人受傷。[2]<br />\n<br />\n警方於案件發生後，對事件動機並無頭緒，並承認由於目擊證人不多，而行兇者及受害人無直接關係，調查有難度"},{"pid":"4679a021fb81095406e42f46137c86e6d7c03f5e","tid":1704062,"uid":10201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"4851aee5731dcb9ccab6f687d2140bcc4abe4929","tid":1704062,"uid":83557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:19:33.000Z","msg":"成10年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家大把天眼"},{"pid":"bc4c508af872c4f4d439d0c3f7c67daf78a4dafc","tid":1704062,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JX11OPt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJX11OPt.jpg&h=c6281128&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KHEuXHO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKHEuXHO.jpg&h=a430b3b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0uxMfuv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0uxMfuv.jpg&h=6adbf6a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc60540a39ee38777970beba0956eccaf6eecd35","tid":1704062,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:20:08.000Z","msg":"CHINA<br />\n- Complete withdrawal of extradition bill<br />\n- Holistic withdrawal of unjust charges<br />\n- Independent commission of inquiry<br />\n- No riot labeling<br />\n- Authentic universal suffrage<br />\n<br />\nC.H